sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant V as Verifier
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    note over W, CA: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Credential Key
    W->>W: Create Evidence<br/>(incl. Credential Key PoP)
    W->>V: Request Attestation (Evidence)
    V->>V: Appraise Evidence
    V->>V: Compute Attestation Results
    V->>W: Return<br/>Attestation Results
    W->>W: Create Credential Request<br/>(incl. Credential Key PoP<br/>and Attesation Results)
    W->>CA: Request Credential (Credential Request)
    CA->>CA: Convert Attestation Results<br/>to Credential Attributes
    CA->>CA: Create and Sign Credential
    CA->>W: Return Credential
